Changelog for corsika simulation tools (developed for VTS simulations)
======================================================================
(log started only in August 2013)

2014/10/18      GM    v.1.41    minor fix to write out first interaction height correctly

2013/10/18	HF    v.1.40	added support for reading in extinction information in another format.
			        added smoother veritas atmospheres (61, 62) and extinction files.

2013/08/15  (HF&GM)   v.1.30    increased precision of photon angles
                                (produced features on the camera)
